{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"66bc83a2-197d-4413-978e-0f675b2caa02","content":"The directory is empty, so no repo-specific docs to draw from. Here's the recommended setup:\n\n---\n\n### 1. Project file — `MyTests.csproj`\n\n```xml\n<Project Sdk=\"Microsoft.NET.Sdk\">\n  <PropertyGroup>\n    <TargetFramework>net8.0</TargetFramework>\n    <EnableMSTestRunner>true</EnableMSTestRunner>\n    <OutputType>Exe</OutputType>\n  </PropertyGroup>\n  <ItemGroup>\n    <PackageReference Include=\"MSTest\" Version=\"3.*\" />\n  </ItemGroup>\n</Project>\n```\n\n`EnableMSTestRunner` + `OutputType Exe` gives you the modern MSTest runner (no `dotnet test` wrapper needed — the test project *is* the test host).\n\n### 2. Enable parallel execution — `Assembly.cs`\n\n```csharp\n[assembly: Parallelize(Scope = ExecutionScope.ClassLevel)]\n```\n\nThis runs **each test class** on its own thread. Use `ExecutionScope.MethodLevel` if you want even more granularity (methods within a class also run in parallel).\n\n### 3. Sequential database tests — use `[DoNotParallelize]`\n\n```csharp\n[TestClass]\n[DoNotParallelize]\npublic class DatabaseIntegrationTests\n{\n    [TestMethod]\n    public void Can_Insert_Record() { /* ... */ }\n\n    [TestMethod]\n    public void Can_Read_Back_Record() { /* ... */ }\n}\n```\n\nClasses marked `[DoNotParallelize]` are pulled out of the parallel pool and run sequentially **after** all parallel classes finish.\n\n---\n\n### How it works together\n\n| Phase | What runs | Threads |\n|-------|-----------|---------|\n| 1 | All classes **without** `[DoNotParallelize]` | parallel (one thread per class) |\n| 2 | All classes **with** `[DoNotParallelize]` | one at a time, sequentially |\n\n### Key points\n\n- **No `.runsettings` file needed** — the attributes handle everything.\n- If you have *multiple* sequential test classes, they all run in phase 2, one after another.\n- `[DoNotParallelize]` can also go on a single `[TestMethod]` if only one test in an otherwise-parallel class needs isolation.","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"7b5c0346-d35e-4fbb-bb1e-1c14fb30ee23","outputTokens":569,"requestId":"1BC3:19BA48:223CA98:260704F:6A03DA76"},"id":"7331d390-d282-42ec-9752-07b0ea53ca7f","timestamp":"2026-05-13T01:57:24.050Z","parentId":"2a033165-4576-4d16-a992-1b7b3484f429"}
